  "instructions": [
    "preheat oven to 425f (220c).",
    "roll out pizza dough to a thickness of 1/4 inch (6 mm).",
    "brush crust with olive oil and sprinkle with salt.",
    "spread miso paste evenly over the dough, leaving a 1/2 inch (1 cm) border around the edges.",
    "sprinkle doner meat, garlic, onion, and peperoncino over the miso paste.",
    "top with mozzarella shreds and chopped basil.",
    "bake for 15-20 minutes or until crust is golden brown and cheese is melted and bubbly."
